{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Increase funding for teacher training & equipment to support left-handed pupils",
        "additional_details": "I call for the Government to give more funding to schools so they can buy left-handed equipment, and fund improved training so teachers are equipped to fully support their left-handed pupils.",
        "background": "As a left-hander, when I was at school, the school didn't have any left-handed books for writing or left-handed scissors for cutting, forcing me to use my right hand for the tasks. This can result in under-developed writing skills, and under-development in sports.",
